import React from "react";
import { Box, FormControl, InputLabel, Input, FormHelperText, TextField, Container } from '@mui/material';

const ContactForm = () => {
    return(
        <Container maxWidth="xs">
        <Box
          sx={{
            mt: 20,
            display: "flex",
            flexDirection: "column",
            alignItems: "center",
          }}
        >
        <FormControl>
            <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            /*helperText="Please enter your name"*/
            id="name"
            label="Full Name"
            autoFocus
            />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
        <TextField
              margin="normal"
              required
              fullWidth
              id="email"
              label="Email Address"
              name="email"
              autoFocus
              /*value={email}
        onChange={(e) => setEmail(e.target.value)}*/
            />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
            <TextField
            id="textarea"
            label="Message"
            placeholder="message"
            multiline
            />
        </FormControl>
        </Box>
        </Container>
    );
}

export default ContactForm;
